query: SELECT c.id as centreId, c.name as centreName, fl.id as floorLevelId, fl.levelName, fl.mapImageUrl FROM shopping_centres c LEFT JOIN floor_levels fl ON fl.centreId = c.id WHERE c.name LIKE '%Chullora%';
